something about when things go wrong.

00:39:06.444 --> 00:39:07.277
Now,

00:39:08.557 --> 00:39:09.974
when I was young,

00:39:11.694 --> 00:39:15.953
I was told that space
is the final frontier

00:39:15.953 --> 00:39:17.871
from watching Star Trek.

