and in a single column 100,000 neurons

00:39:54.182 --> 00:39:55.765
and that adds up to

00:39:58.034 --> 00:40:02.276
at the end, billions of
synapses in a single column.

00:40:02.276 --> 00:40:04.194
But there's another kind of network,

00:40:04.194 --> 00:40:06.112
and that's a communication network.

00:40:06.112 --> 00:40:08.664
A communication network
